game.description:
Are you a type of girl who loves to play with the Barbie princess? Do you also like to be known as a Popstar fan? If yes, Barbie And Popstar Dress Up game is just for you. Today in this brand new dressing game for girls, you will meet with the gorgeous Keira and beautiful Tori who are happy for their new events. These both cuties are good friends and like music very much, so they have decided to rock the stage together in the tonight. Help them pick up some cool matching dresses!
Remember this event is going to be the most awaited gig of the summer season. Everything right from the fabulous choreography to the wonderful stage decorations is ready except the preparation of their matching costumes. You have joined this html5 girls game as their stylist and help both the girls to create the awesome outfits. Make sure that Keira collect her magic microphone and Tori carries her favorite magic hairbrush. Mix and match as many cool outfits as you can to help Olivia Princess and Olivia Popstar find their desired dresses!
They both are popular stars so it is your responsibilities to put your best fashion sense to the test to make both of them look awesome. People love to see their favorite stars wearing special outfits. Go through their wardrobe and prepare the one by one to attain the desired looks! We are pretty sure that you are lucky enough to give them a complete makeover and enjoy a special look. Apply the eye shadow, lipstick and face powder to make their faces glow! All the best to play more dress up games online on atmegame.com, no download required!
